import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"all-styling-properties"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#all-styling-properties"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`All styling properties`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"a"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#a"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`A`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"f"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#f"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`F`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"Flex.md"}}>{`flex`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Reach out with questions via our `}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"https://slack.viewsdx.com/"}}>{`Slack Questions Channel`}</MDXTag>{`.
Mention `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`@tom`}</MDXTag>{` or `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`@dario`}</MDXTag>{` to make sure that we get your notifications.`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
